{"Id":480224,"Title":"书带轩诗为郑同夫赋","Dynasty":"明","Author":"刘崧","Context":"读书何所，西山之阳。崇轩朝跻，其云苍苍。有草有草，垂带而厉。匪伊垂之，君子所萟。濯以甘雨，扬之谷风。有蔚其苗，则靡所同。人亦有言，匪韭匪薤。不有君子，孰曰书带。在昔孔圣，仰钻庖羲。或韦其编，亦三绝之。我乐我书，爰启其纽。我其藏之，或系于肘。相彼良苗，亦绵其藨。譬之树兰，毋混彼艾萧。我思不其，远而莫至。宜尔孙子，是有是似。尚勿剪薙之，以蕃厥世。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"95442e695ff007ab064b0e397cd347e7","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6506273,"Sentence":"有草有草，垂带而厉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu cǎo yǒu cǎo ，chuǐ dài ér lì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506274,"Sentence":"匪伊垂之，君子所萟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fěi yī chuǐ zhī ，jūn zi suǒ yì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506275,"Sentence":"濯以甘雨，扬之谷风。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhuó yi gān yǔ ，yáng zhī gǔ fēng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506276,"Sentence":"有蔚其苗，则靡所同。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu wèi jī miáo ，zé mǐ suǒ tóng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506277,"Sentence":"人亦有言，匪韭匪薤。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rén yì yǒu yán ，fěi jiu fěi xiè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506278,"Sentence":"不有君子，孰曰书带。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú yǒu jūn zi ，shú yuē shū dài ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506279,"Sentence":"在昔孔圣，仰钻庖羲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zài xī kǒng shèng ，yǎng zuān páo xī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506280,"Sentence":"或韦其编，亦三绝之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huò wéi jī biān ，yì sān jué zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":9,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506281,"Sentence":"我乐我书，爰启其纽。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ lè wǒ shū ，yuán qi jī niu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506282,"S